In each dir:

* transparent - a text file with the hex code for the transparent colour

* font.png - the font to be used
* altfont.png - the font with colours inverted or changed for highlight

* splash.png - splash screen

* first.png - first screen background
* loop.png - the loop screen background

some good fonts: aqui, terminal bold, space marine, origami mommy 9, clean, courier 10 pitch
